('### BULO 2: "Ya sabemos la fecha exacta de inicio"
A fecha de compilación de este manual **NO** se conoce la fecha exacta de apertura del plazo. Se sabe que será en **ABRIL de 2026**, pero no se sabe si será el 1, el 10 o el 15 de abril. Muchas personas en redes sociales afirman conocer la fecha exacta: **ES MENTIRA**. La fecha se conocerá con la publicación en el BOE.', '[-0.022327926,0.018122325,0.02962758,-0.055096556,0.008604262,0.021954406,0.0053928965,-0.0034560792,-0.011519418,0.028043656,-0.037830997,-0.0025076861,0.004024521,0.022450162,0.12257866,0.018208556,0.004006077,-0.0013480344,-0.021634718,-0.013444038,0.0033751037,0.013473622,-0.0007849221,-0.012201674,-0.008849955,0.012649347,0.009461749,-0.001347818,0.021501526,-0.007399773,-0.008799247,-0.017486708,0.009343708,0.029435853,-0.0043805316,0.029973209,0.032683562,-0.0031961927,0.010079518,0.026209818,-0.012238485,-0.009220996,-0.008470108,-0.032728422,0.0072125504,-0.016148057,-0.029866323,-0.0255314,-0.011028021,0.029342335,-0.024991864,-0.015604887,-0.030095618,-0.15230252,-0.02773465,0.0036596688,-0.0057607987,0.04191115,-0.002888144,-0.016353339,-0.037970893,0.026736178,-0.022273635,-0.0047816327,-0.01885727,-0.009162757,-0.025734887,4.8364738e-05,-0.0148819,-0.0037066669,-0.015227471,-0.02980985,-0.0036189135,-0.0008756353,0.011386837,-0.02112136,-0.005329323,0.023588745,-0.00675005,-0.014277723,-0.028636467,-0.017217197,-0.025720013,-0.0068409424,-0.017958997,-0.014025696,0.014481743,-0.021337561,-0.015716692,-0.018893784,-0.02204351,0.023599193,-0.029149758,-0.028172884,-0.002487747,-0.0069866506,-0.008013696,-0.010253308,-0.004791664,-0.032855283,0.004738028,-0.0155057125,-0.027122052,-0.017645773,0.034693353,-0.006015805,-0.004611498,0.012016198,0.0005292432,0.007816437,-0.009066192,-0.0024071652,0.012402691,0.0009392205,-0.0056202235,-0.13831592,0.007944415,0.005697699,-0.019516757,-0.0071642953,0.005459373,-0.024664495,-0.017383963,-0.015447514,-0.0060227704,-0.0027462165,0.007776876,-0.016743306,0.009050232,0.004431359,0.009810545,-0.007