('## 5. Documentación necesaria
### 5.1. Pasaporte (o cédula de inscripción)
- Se debe presentar el pasaporte **COMPLETO**: **TODAS** las páginas, no solo la página con la foto y los datos. Extranjería necesita revisar página por página para comprobar sellos de entrada y salida, especialmente para verificar los 5 meses de estancia.
- **PASAPORTE NO VIGENTE:** Se está negociando que para este procedimiento extraordinario no sea obligatorio que el pasaporte esté vigente, ya que renovar un pasaporte en muchos países lleva mucho tiempo y no todos pueden trasladarse a Madrid (donde están la mayoría de consulados y embajadas). Esto forma parte del acuerdo principal, pendiente de confirmación en el BOE.
- **SOLICITANTES DE ASILO:** Pueden tener dificultades con el pasaporte. Se espera que se contemple su situación especial.
- **SI NO TIENES PASAPORTE:** Se puede obtener una **CÉDULA DE INSCRIPCIÓN**. El procedimiento es:
1. Acudir a un notario.
2. El notario escribe a la embajada o consulado del país de origen.
3. Si no se recibe respuesta en unos días, se emite un extracto notarial.
4. Con ese extracto se puede solicitar la cédula de inscripción.
5. La cédula de inscripción tiene una validez de 1 año y se puede renovar demostrando que se sigue en la misma situación que impedía obtener el pasaporte.', '[0.02246267,0.0016805818,0.010474845,-0.039722513,0.020134654,0.023374107,0.0022138648,0.01547202,0.0056755496,0.011523138,-0.021615276,0.0034523245,-0.0030177014,0.027081681,0.15450892,0.013052623,-0.0012711798,0.01778411,0.005152614,-0.01970732,0.041310683,-0.0024120796,-0.009937271,-0.009105422,-0.014450604,0.009124563,0.0035314793,0.016215153,0.02172328,-0.024638822,-0.002649672,-0.00389829,-0.012365154,0.026094796,0.0056326236,0.037804905,0.007990749,-0.0063245487,-0.008378958,-0.016527327,0.010570253,-0.007901101,-0.0024993233,-0.009328093,0.009421235,-0.021132475,-0.0032971182,0.0042642537,-0.02987473,0.020418372,-0.0017405028,-0.021629773,-0.018952277,-0.17845327,-0.017114948,-0.025938459,0.004389354,-0.004977503,0.0003162405,-0.029008003,-0.017720418,0.022762464,-0.012410273,-0.0013769213,0.0018068515,0.01263633,-0.028833648,0.033285882,0.0056054066,0.00023054508,-0.011954258,0.009266954,0.0050239745,-0.020309987,0.010869432,-0.040302273,-0.005420474,-0.0074948054,-0.0023973454,-0.024239795,-0.01679213,-0.0052567734,-0.003023776,-0.0021115842,0.024131918,-0.02742028,0.01634211,0.019432653,0.00096463674,0.013992605,-0.004337914,0.013455068,0.030417664,-0.020076327,0.006736852,-0.013382153,-0.0022784697,0.025043145,0.008625359,-0.017159041,-0.0045298645,-0.042128064,0.00041644785,-0.005597401,0.026553981,-0.012845152,0.0139805125,0.04280431,-7.1440096e-05,-0.00033759366,-0.004059714,-0.010937288,-0.03215156,0.027923264,0.01828363,-0.12338501,-0.0011956122,0.00782771,0.0005673781,-0.022444451,0.004130562,-0.001327114,0.012658648,-0.0083198445,0.00601736,-0.0007350138,-0.0008986986,-0.015355044,-1.6007758e-05,-0.03466204,-0.0057182955,-0.009989186,0.017368153,0.010310833,0.0010143716,-0.008046911,-0.021268018,-0.018790143,0.042414624,-0.009312387,-0.017000627,0.0031871207,-0.0042792535,-0.019721402,0.01756